attributionInfo.brokerName: Berkshire Hathaway HomeServices Carolina Premier Properties
Berkshire Hathaway HomeServices Carolina Premier Properties

data.description: Back on the market at a new and improved price! Ready for some front porch sitting? Well the sellers are ready to sell! Enjoy a nice breeze and the Intracoastal Waterway view. Not too big, not too small - this home has a large living room,  kitchen dining space, as well as a dedicated dining room. Some of the extras include - laundry room, pantry, attached garage, detached garage/workshop with two outdoor awnings. Best of all, the location is super close to Holden Beach and an easy trip to Shallotte. Broker is related to seller.
